    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/1c98fcf63cb0d68b440c49ec570bc2c3.avif?t=1707744416\" width=533 height=78 /></span><br>一头扎进这款 3D 动作/赛车游戏，全速奔跑，跳跃躲避危险，冲向终点！有 30 多个不同的关卡在等着你，每个关卡都有任务和奖牌等着你去赢得。您不会缺少挑战！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/9b3363027aee936c82cb69d42eaf4297.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/9b3363027aee936c82cb69d42eaf4297.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Help Voulpy in his adventure！</strong>[/h2］他的小弟弟被绑架了，你要穿越各个世界找到他！海滩、丛林、雪山、火焰地牢，但要小心不要成为螃蟹的诱饵哦<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/course.gif\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span>[/img］<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为岛屿上最酷的海怪！</strong></h2>游戏中有多种服装可以解锁，海盗或独角兽--这取决于你的选择。<br>因此，如果您喜欢章鱼、海滩和冒险，那就在《海怪奥德赛》中开始冒险吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/3d3f449fab0587ae5ab8d92feaa460c2.poster.avif?t=1707744416\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/3d3f449fab0587ae5ab8d92feaa460c2.webm?t=1707744416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112260/extras/73c310eb9c727f0cfc4761b49dabb095.avif?t=1707744416\" width=515 height=245 /></span></h2>",
